description.content:
Only pass the fields that you want to update. If you want to unset a specific editable field, pass `null`.
Note that you cannot unset the `name` field, which is mandatory.

If you want to set the caller ID name and the name of given phone number, you can provide the following body:
```
{
  "callerIdName": "Jawn Dough",
  "name": "TMBG Dial-A-Song Line"
}
```

If you want to unset the caller ID name, pass the following instead:
```
{
  "callerIdName": null
}
```

Moreover, you may set the route to an extension for a given phone number, with the following request body:
```
{
  "routeTo": {
    "id": "458e38ae-f468-11eb-9a03-0242ac130003",
    "type": "EXTENSION"
  }  
}
```

If you want to unset the route, pass the following instead
```
{
  "routeTo": null
}
```

You can provide the following request body to set the billing group id:
```
{
  "billingGroupId": "768e38ae-f468-11eb-9a03-0242ac131234"
}
```

To unset the billing group id, pass the following:
```
{
  "billingGroupId": null
}
```

