description.content:
Update Find me/Follow me data for a specific extension.
This endpoint should be used for setting up the fields for the following use cases:
  - If no answer, send to.
  - If call fails, send to.

Only pass the fields that you want to update.
If you want to forward unanswered calls to an external phone number, you can use the following request body:

```
{
  "finalStep": {
    "action": "EXTERNAL_NUMBER",
    "externalNumber": "+15145552672"
  }
}
```

If you want to forward unanswered calls to an extension, you can use:

```
{
  "finalStep": {
    "action": "EXTENSION",
    "extensionId": "458e38ae-f468-11eb-9a03-0242ac130003"
  }
}
```

You can also forward failed calls to either an extension

```
{
  "unavailableStep": {
    "extensionId": "458e38ae-f468-11eb-9a03-0242ac130003"
  }
}
```

Or an external phone number:

```
{
  "unavailableStep": {
    "externalNumber": "+15145552672"
  }
}
```

Finally, you can also unset the value of the `unavailableStep` field by sending `null`:

```
{
  "unavailableStep": null
}
```
<br>

### Authentication Scopes

`voice-admin.v1.write` must be used when a token is requested from the Authentication API.

